Description: Functions for discordant kinship modeling (and other sibling-based quasi-experimental designs). Contains data restructuring functions and functions for generating biometrically informed data for kin pairs. See [Garrison and Rodgers, 2021 <>], [Sims, Trattner, and Garrison, 2024 <>) for empirical examples.
URL: https://github.com/R-Computing-Lab/discord,
    https://r-computing-lab.github.io/discord/
